        </ab></refsDecl></encodingDesc><revisionDesc status="approved"><change who="KI MAM" when="2015-10-01">Kollationiert</change><change who="KI MAM" when="2017-05-12">Kollationiert</change><change who="MAM" when="2018-07-15">Überführt aus Bahr–Schnitzler-Daten</change><change who="MAM" when="2019-01-20">Index check</change></revisionDesc></teiHeader><facsimile><graphic url="HS_AM60162Ba"/><graphic url="HS_AM60162Ba_R"/></facsimile><text type="card"><body><div type="address"><address><addrLine><pb facs="HS_AM60162Ba"/>Herrn </addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype">Hermann Bahr</hi></addrLine><addrLine><rs ref="#pmb165" type="place">Wien Ober St. Veit</rs></addrLine><addrLine><rs ref="#pmb220" type="place">Veitlissengasse</rs></addrLine></address></div><div type="image" n="1"><figure><graphic url="./images/HS_AM60162Ba" width="9cm"/></figure></div><div type="writingSession" n="1"><p><salute>herzlichen Dank, lieber Hermann </salute>für dein neues <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="KL124-3"/><rs type="work" ref="#pmb30035" subtype="implied">B<damage agent="hole"><supplied>uc</supplied></damage>h</rs><note type="commentary" xml:id="KL124-3h"><bibl><rs ref="#pmb10815" type="person">Hermann Bahr</rs>: <rs ref="#pmb30035" type="work">Inventur</rs>. Berlin: <rs ref="#pmb29639" type="org">S. Fischer</rs><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><date>1912</date></bibl>.</note> u viele Grüße. Ob die dich <damage agent="hole"><supplied>tre</supplied></damage>ffen werden, weiss ich nicht – denn niemand weiss <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="KL124-2"/>wo du bist<note type="commentary" xml:id="KL124-2h"><rs ref="#pmb10815" type="person">Bahr</rs> war zumindest seit <date>Mitte September</date> mehrere Wochen in der <rs ref="#pmb144" type="place">Villa Mautner</rs>.</note>. So sei denn der Findigkeit der Post <pb facs="HS_AM60162Ba_R"/>vertraut. Au<damage agent="hole"><supplied>f</supplied></damage> bald!</p><closer>Dein <signed>Arthur </signed></closer><postscript><p><date><anchor type="commentary" xml:id="KL124-1"/>26/9 1912<note type="commentary" xml:id="KL124-1h">Der Poststempel widerspricht der Datierung.</note></date></p></postscript></div></body></text></TEI>